'''Nolan Ramsay North''' ([[31 October|October 31]], [[1970]]) is an accomplished actor and voice actor, with many video-game and television credits.

==Roles==
* [[2017]]: ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of War]]'' - [[Isildur]], Tarandor, Zog, Nemesis Orcs, Humans
* [[2014]]: ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of Mordor]]'' - Black Hand 
* [[2011]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: War in the North]]'' - [[Eradan (video game character)|Eradan]]
* [[2009]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: Conquest]]'': Evil Human Officer #2 / Gondorian Officer #2
* [[2006]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II: The Rise of the Witch-king]]'': Additional voices
* [[2006]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II]]'': Additional voices
